data.meta_description: Clint Absher (24) M  - 2016: Appeared in 19 matches for the Lutes and started eight of them. Recorded five goals on the season and 14 shots on goal, including three
data.text:
2016: Appeared in 19 matches for the Lutes and started eight of them. Recorded five goals on the season and 14 shots on goal, including three against Pomona-Pitzer and four against George Fox.

2015: Played in 12 matches for the Lutes, appearing in 10 wins with four shots on goal.

2014: Played in 20 matches for the Lutes, making 13 starts. Recorded two goals and two assists, including one game-winner.

High School: Earned second team all South Puget Sound League soccer honors his junor year. Also competed in basketball and spent two years as basketball team captain.

Personal: Born on July 1, 1994 to parents Dan and Kappy, who played soccer at PLU Is a brother to Larissa, Karly, Kailani, Tad, Talia, and Rob.
